Type: Package
Package: dyno
Title: A Toolkit for Inferring, Interpreting and Visualising Single-Cell Trajectories
Description: A collection of R packages aimed at supporting the trajectory inference community on multiple levels, 
  both end-users who want to apply trajectory inference on their dataset of interest, 
  as well as developers who seek to easily quantify the performance of their 
  trajectory inference method and compare it to other methods. Saelens and Cannoodt et
  al. (2019) <doi:10.1038/s41587-019-0071-9>.
Version: 0.2.0
